msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.276:0.2"
msgid "28. Rāgapeyyāla "
msgstr "28. Abbreviated Texts Beginning with Greed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: catuiddhipādasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.276:0.3"
msgid "276. Iddhipādasutta "
msgstr "276. Bases of Psychic Power "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.276:1.1"
msgid "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "“For insight into greed, four things should be developed. "

msgctxt "an4.276:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.276:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an4.276:1.4"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe … cittasamādhi … pe … vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. "
msgstr "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy … mental development … inquiry, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an4.276:1.5"
msgid "Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "For insight into greed, these four things should be developed.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.276:1.6"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

